on it if you want to time something.

156
00:11:15,782 --> 00:11:18,478
If you're looking for a larger set,
those have built-in videos...

157
00:11:18,551 --> 00:11:20,951
which are extremely convenient.

158
00:11:22,155 --> 00:11:24,419
He's not gonna buy.
You're wasting your time.

159
00:11:24,491 --> 00:11:28,951
Beat it. Scram. Go away and don't
come back. Don't write, don't call.

160
00:11:29,028 --> 00:11:32,122
Did you get my messages?
I need to talk to you. It's important.

161
00:11:32,198 --> 00:11:34,257
- Let me buy you lunch.
- No.

162
00:11:36,002 --> 00:11:38,869
Dinner then, please. This is important.
I have things to talk to you about.

163
00:11:38,938 --> 00:11:40,872
I had things to say to you,
but I don't anymore.

164
00:11:40,940 --> 00:11:43,170
Don't say that.

165
00:11:43,243 --> 00:11:45,370
Things are different now. It's nice.

166
00:11:45,445 --> 00:11:48,778
No more waiting up for you, no calls
in the middle of the night, no excuses.

167
00:11:48,848 --> 00:11:52,409
Linda, look at me.

168
00:11:52,485 --> 00:11:54,146
That's not me anymore.

169
00:11:54,220 --> 00:11:56,882
I've got a plan big enough
to change everything for us.

170
00:11:56,956 --> 00:11:59,823
- Please.
- Come on, please. Let me say my piece.

171
00:12:06,266 --> 00:12:11,203
What if I can sell this guy a TV?
Not that 13" job, but that 60" TV there.

172
00:12:11,271 --> 00:12:14,763
- Will you have dinner with me then?
- That man's too cheap to buy a toaster.

173
00:12:18,778 --> 00:12:20,803
Are you kidding me?

174
00:12:21,948 --> 00:12:23,381
Deal?

175
00:12:26,452 --> 00:12:28,443
A piece of cake.

176
00:12:30,456 --> 00:12:31,889
Ouch.

177
00:12:34,661 --> 00:12:37,459
