to this baby, Commander.

178
00:12:37,530 --> 00:12:39,464
It might suck you right in.

179
00:12:39,532 --> 00:12:41,295
Beautiful.

180
00:12:41,367 --> 00:12:44,666
How are you? Dave Kelly,
sales representative for Sony.

181
00:12:45,572 --> 00:12:47,699
Just lookin'.

182
00:12:47,774 --> 00:12:51,141
Well, aren't we all.
It's okay. I'm not working today.

183
00:12:51,210 --> 00:12:54,202
